---

<aside class="timezone-notice" role="note">
  <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true">CL</span>
  <div class="body">
    <p class="primary">Todos los horarios estan en <strong>Hora de Chile (GMT-4)</strong>.</p>
    <p class="hint">Los horarios pueden cambiar segun FIFA.</p>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .timezone-notice {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .icon {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(7, 23, 53, 0.18);
    color: var(--pm-blue-900);
    font-size: 0.54rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .body {
    display: flex;
    min-width: 0;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.04rem;
  }

  .primary {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--pm-blue-900);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .hint {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--pm-blue-700);
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
